text:
@NYGovCuomo Andrew, we "fight every way we can to save every life we can", not because we are Americans; not because we are New Yorkers; but because (inside the womb, and outside the womb) (with or without #coronavirus) we are human beings!
https://t.co/61uAZdp4mb
